      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy runabout. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is, and with a bit of TLC it could be a great little car for the right person. I believe in being straightforward, so if you want an honest car at a sensible price, come take a look.",
